<h3 id="podcasts">
<a class="heading-anchor" href="#podcasts" hidden><svg width="16" height="16"><use xlink:href="https://thisweek.gnome.org/images/icons.svg#anchor"></use></svg></a>Podcasts <a href="https://gitlab.gnome.org/World/podcasts"><svg width='16' height='16'><use xlink:href='https://thisweek.gnome.org/images/icons.svg#link'></use></svg></a>
</h3><p>Podcast app for GNOME.</p>
<p><a href="https://matrix.to/#/@alatiera:matrix.org">Jordan Petridis</a> says</p>
<blockquote>
<p>After more than a year of development, the GTK 4 port of Podcasts has been merged. Huge thanks to Christopher Davis and Maximiliano for the joined effort of porting the codebase, but as well to Bilal Elmoussaoui and Julian Hofer for the exhaustive reviews.</p>
<p>We are putting the finishing touches still but you will be able to enjoy a new release o Podcasts in the month ahead.

<img src="https://thisweek.gnome.org/posts/2022/07/twig-54/HkXHiZNnEzCSswnBIxewqwsZ.png" alt="" />


